**Example 1: 失败示例**

AI任务不存在

Input: 

```
tccli iss DescribeAITaskResult --cli-unfold-argument  \
    --TaskId at**********************1 \
    --ChannelId ********************** \
    --DetectType Pet
```

Output: 
```
{
    "Response": {
        "Error": {
            "Code": "ResourceNotFound.AITaskNotExisted",
            "Message": "AI任务不存在"
        },
        "RequestId": "1bd31583-6bd4-486c-8ae3-1844cf4e6d1e"
    }
}
```
